    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"658873\">Lessness</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/252551-graph-theory/topic/Question.20about.20the.20degree-sum.20formula/near/453457012\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Can <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Finset/Sym.html#Sym2.instFintype\">this</a> be used?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes, it will be used if you have <code>Fintype V</code> in context. (That's what Yakov is saying, but I wanted to state it directly.)</p>",
